{"tid":764288,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"報道指Tesla上海新廠將投資390億　並會在中國集資","createTime":"2018-08-02T00:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T03:33:39.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"028e84db0d456d76233d3c46d0e585dfe95dbe6f","tid":764288,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1706578/org/d0b9ce26154d229eb83411ff38a4c8b0.JPG/hlxu2F_podqeDwUhhA_Oa2R8Zo1AWMWipdZpmqXWaZo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1706578%2Forg%2Fd0b9ce26154d229eb83411ff38a4c8b0.JPG%2Fhlxu2F_podqeDwUhhA_Oa2R8Zo1AWMWipdZpmqXWaZo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dff64773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTesla早前公布在上海臨港建立中國首個生產基地，已經簽署了投資協議，但並未公布詳情。有報指出，Tesla將會投資50億美元（約390億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述熟知事件的人士報道，Tesla計劃投資50億美元，該公司正考慮在中國籌集資金，作為工廠的部份投資。<br />\n<br />\n該消息人士又表示，上海工廠預計在2020年投產，將會生產公司熱門車款Model 3電動車。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：鄭寶生<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/217703/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87tesla%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%A0%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87390%E5%84%84-%E4%B8%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F217703%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%258C%2587tesla%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587390%25E5%2584%2584-%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%2587&d=iaCHxBfwVEno7mE5ptD2yGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=d83494cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/217703/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87tesla%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%A0%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87390%E5%84%84-%E4%B8%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87</a>"},{"